title: Come join us in oceanic league community

embed.description: Step up your game with a modern voice & text chat app. Crystal clear voice, multiple server and channel support, mobile apps, and more. Get your free server now!

body: Come join us in discord for some fun time and for learning experiences, need help with game play and strategies? no problem, our community is here to help. Just joining because youre bored? no problem, we are active and love to chat. Everyone and anyone is welcome, invite your friends and lets all help create a friendly and active community. https://discord.gg/E2J6Wq8
